metadata.name: Metlifecare Limited
metadata.description: Metlifecare Limited engages in the developing, owning, and operating of retirement villages and care homes for the elderly in New Zealand. The company offers independent living homes, care apartments, and care beds and suites. As of June 30, 2020, it owns and operates a portfolio of 25 villages. Metlifecare Limited was founded in 1984 and is based in Auckland, New Zealand. As of November 3, 2020, Metlifecare Limited was taken private.
